| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1016 — Recovery Inhibition (hive)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 1508d676-39a3-5795-bae2-0e3a6812d0f7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
